{
  "video_id": "Mt0PiXLvYlU",
  "title": "Sci-fi stories that imagine a future Africa | Nnedi Okorafor",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 12760.0,
      "end_time": 15976.0,
      "text": "What if an African girl from a traditional family"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 16000.0,
      "end_time": 18136.0,
      "text": "in a part of future Africa"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 18160.0,
      "end_time": 21896.0,
      "text": "is accepted into the finest university in the galaxy,"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 21920.0,
      "end_time": 23200.0,
      "text": "planets away?"
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 24280.0,
      "end_time": 25840.0,
      "text": "What if she decides to go?"
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 27360.0,
      "end_time": 30400.0,
      "text": "This is an excerpt from my \"Binti\" novella trilogy:"
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 32119.0,
      "end_time": 35576.0,
      "text": "I powered up the transporter and said a silent prayer."
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 35600.0,
      "end_time": 38856.0,
      "text": "I had no idea what I was going to do if it didn&#39;t work."
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 38880.0,
      "end_time": 40296.0,
      "text": "My transporter was cheap,"
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 40320.0,
      "end_time": 43896.0,
      "text": "so even a droplet of moisture or, more likely, a grain of sand,"
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 43920.0,
      "end_time": 45776.0,
      "text": "would cause it to short."
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 45800.0,
      "end_time": 49560.0,
      "text": "It was faulty, and most of the time I had to restart it over and over"
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 49800.0,
      "end_time": 50296.0,
      "text": "before it worked."
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 50320.0,
      "end_time": 53536.0,
      "text": "\"Please not now, please not now,\" I thought."
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 53560.0,
      "end_time": 57176.0,
      "text": "The transporter shivered in the sand and I held my breath."
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 57200.0,
      "end_time": 59496.0,
      "text": "Tiny, flat and black as a prayer stone,"
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 59520.0,
      "end_time": 62760.0,
      "text": "it buzzed softly and then slowly rose from the sand."
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 63760.0,
      "end_time": 66256.0,
      "text": "Finally, it produced the baggage-lifting force."
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 66280.0,
      "end_time": 67816.0,
      "text": "I grinned."
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 67840.0,
      "end_time": 69920.0,
      "text": "Now I could make it to the shuttle on time."
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 71360.0,
      "end_time": 75696.0,
      "text": "I swiped otjize from my forehead with my index finger and knelt down,"
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 75720.0,
      "end_time": 77576.0,
      "text": "then I touched the finger to the sand,"
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 77600.0,
      "end_time": 80560.0,
      "text": "grounding the sweet-smelling red clay into it."
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 80800.0,
      "end_time": 81960.0,
      "text": "\"Thank you,\" I whispered."
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 83400.0,
      "end_time": 86160.0,
      "text": "It was a half-mile walk along the dark desert road."
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 86400.0,
      "end_time": 88800.0,
      "text": "With the transporter working I would make it there on time."
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 90800.0,
      "end_time": 92816.0,
      "text": "Straightening up, I paused and shut my eyes."
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 92840.0,
      "end_time": 96736.0,
      "text": "Now, the weight of my entire life was pressing on my shoulders."
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 96760.0,
      "end_time": 99976.0,
      "text": "I was defying the most traditional part of myself for the first time"
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 100000.0,
      "end_time": 101576.0,
      "text": "in my entire life."
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 101600.0,
      "end_time": 105735.0,
      "text": "I was leaving in the dead of night, and they had no clue."
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 105760.0,
      "end_time": 109416.0,
      "text": "My nine siblings, all older than me except for my younger sister and brother,"
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 109440.0,
      "end_time": 111456.0,
      "text": "would never see this coming."
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 111480.0,
      "end_time": 114840.0,
      "text": "My parents would never imagine I&#39;d do such a thing in a million years."
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 115640.0,
      "end_time": 119416.0,
      "text": "By the time they all realized what I&#39;d done and where I was going,"
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 119440.0,
      "end_time": 120960.0,
      "text": "I&#39;d have left the planet."
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 122840.0,
      "end_time": 125536.0,
      "text": "In my absence, my parents would growl to each other"
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 125560.0,
      "end_time": 128416.0,
      "text": "that I was never to set foot in their home again."
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 128440.0,
      "end_time": 131150.0,
      "text": "My four aunties and two uncles who lived down the road"
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 131390.0,
      "end_time": 133160.0,
      "text": "would shout and gossip amongst themselves"
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 133400.0,
      "end_time": 135720.0,
      "text": "about how I had scandalized the entire bloodline."
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 136360.0,
      "end_time": 137960.0,
      "text": "I was going to be a pariah."
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 139000.0,
      "end_time": 141735.0,
      "text": "\"Go,\" I softly whispered to the transporter,"
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 141759.0,
      "end_time": 143576.0,
      "text": "stamping my foot."
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 143600.0,
      "end_time": 146816.0,
      "text": "The thin metal rings I wore around each ankle jingled noisily,"
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 146840.0,
      "end_time": 148400.0,
      "text": "but I stamped my foot again."
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 149440.0,
      "end_time": 152776.0,
      "text": "Once on, the transporter worked best when I didn&#39;t touch it."
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 152800.0,
      "end_time": 155840.0,
      "text": "\"Go,\" I said again, sweat forming on my brow."
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 156600.0,
      "end_time": 157856.0,
      "text": "When nothing moved,"
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 157880.0,
      "end_time": 162495.0,
      "text": "I chanced giving the two large suitcases sitting atop the force field a shove."
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 162520.0,
      "end_time": 165576.0,
      "text": "They moved smoothly, and I breathed another sigh of relief."
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 165600.0,
      "end_time": 167600.0,
      "text": "At least some luck was on my side."
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 170360.0,
      "end_time": 173776.0,
      "text": "So, in a distant future part of Africa,"
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 173800.0,
      "end_time": 177576.0,
      "text": "Binti is a mathematical genius of the Himba ethnic group."
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 177600.0,
      "end_time": 180296.0,
      "text": "She&#39;s been accepted into a university on another planet,"
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 180320.0,
      "end_time": 181720.0,
      "text": "and she&#39;s decided to go."
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 182760.0,
      "end_time": 184935.0,
      "text": "Carrying the blood of her people in her veins,"
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 184960.0,
      "end_time": 189736.0,
      "text": "adorned with the teachings, ways, even the land on her very skin,"
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 189760.0,
      "end_time": 191280.0,
      "text": "Binti leaves the earth."
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 192480.0,
      "end_time": 196335.0,
      "text": "As the story progresses, she becomes not other, but more."
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 196360.0,
      "end_time": 199536.0,
      "text": "This idea of leaving but bringing and then becoming more"
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 199560.0,
      "end_time": 202456.0,
      "text": "is at one of the hearts of Afrofuturism,"
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 202480.0,
      "end_time": 205440.0,
      "text": "or you can simply call it a different type of science fiction."
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 206920.0,
      "end_time": 211550.0,
      "text": "I can best explain the difference between classic science fiction and Afrofuturism"
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 211800.0,
      "end_time": 213000.0,
      "text": "if I used the octopus analogy."
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 214680.0,
      "end_time": 215896.0,
      "text": "Like humans,"
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 215920.0,
      "end_time": 219950.0,
      "text": "octopuses are some of the most intelligent creatures on earth."
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 219120.0,
      "end_time": 224560.0,
      "text": "However, octopus intelligence evolved from a different evolutionary line,"
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 224800.0,
      "end_time": 226576.0,
      "text": "separate from that of human beings,"
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 226600.0,
      "end_time": 228976.0,
      "text": "so the foundation is different."
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 229000.0,
      "end_time": 232800.0,
      "text": "The same can be said about the foundations of various forms of science fiction."
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 234800.0,
      "end_time": 237456.0,
      "text": "So much of science fiction speculates"
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 237480.0,
      "end_time": 240696.0,
      "text": "about technologies, societies, social issues,"
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 240720.0,
      "end_time": 243736.0,
      "text": "what&#39;s beyond our planet, what&#39;s within our planet."
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 243760.0,
      "end_time": 246736.0,
      "text": "Science fiction is one of the greatest and most effective forms"
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 246760.0,
      "end_time": 248416.0,
      "text": "of political writing."
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 248440.0,
      "end_time": 250800.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s all about the question, \"What if?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 251800.0,
      "end_time": 256736.0,
      "text": "Still, not all science fiction has the same ancestral bloodline,"
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 256760.0,
      "end_time": 259736.0,
      "text": "that line being Western-rooted science fiction,"
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 259760.0,
      "end_time": 261560.0,
      "text": "which is mostly white and male."
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 262200.0,
      "end_time": 265695.0,
      "text": "We&#39;re talking Isaac Asimov, Jules Verne,"
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 265720.0,
      "end_time": 269279.0,
      "text": "H.G. Wells, George Orwell, Robert Heinlein, etc."
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 270839.0,
      "end_time": 274280.0,
      "text": "So what if a Nigerian-American wrote science fiction?"
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 275600.0,
      "end_time": 278896.0,
      "text": "Growing up, I didn&#39;t read much science fiction."
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 278920.0,
      "end_time": 280616.0,
      "text": "I couldn&#39;t relate to these stories"
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 280640.0,
      "end_time": 286216.0,
      "text": "preoccupied with xenophobia, colonization and seeing aliens as others."
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 286240.0,
      "end_time": 289680.0,
      "text": "And I saw no reflection of anyone who looked like me in those narratives."
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 290840.0,
      "end_time": 292376.0,
      "text": "In the \"Binti\" novella trilogy,"
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 292400.0,
      "end_time": 296695.0,
      "text": "Binti leaves the planet to seek education from extraterrestrials."
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 296720.0,
      "end_time": 298456.0,
      "text": "She goes out as she is,"
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 298480.0,
      "end_time": 300136.0,
      "text": "looking the way she looks,"
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 300160.0,
      "end_time": 301776.0,
      "text": "carrying her cultures,"
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 301800.0,
      "end_time": 303240.0,
      "text": "being who she is."
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 304120.0,
      "end_time": 305776.0,
      "text": "I was inspired to write this story"
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 305800.0,
      "end_time": 309976.0,
      "text": "not because I was following a line of classic space opera narratives,"
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 310000.0,
      "end_time": 312336.0,
      "text": "but because of blood that runs deep,"
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 312360.0,
      "end_time": 314976.0,
      "text": "family, cultural conflict"
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 315000.0,
      "end_time": 318640.0,
      "text": "and the need to see an African girl leave the planet on her own terms."
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 320640.0,
      "end_time": 323616.0,
      "text": "My science fiction had different ancestors,"
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 323640.0,
      "end_time": 324840.0,
      "text": "African ones."
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 326560.0,
      "end_time": 328696.0,
      "text": "So I&#39;m Nigerian-American."
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 328720.0,
      "end_time": 331216.0,
      "text": "I was born to two Nigerian immigrant parents"
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 331240.0,
      "end_time": 333376.0,
      "text": "and raised in the United States,"
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 333400.0,
      "end_time": 336960.0,
      "text": "one of the birthplaces of classic science fiction."
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 336120.0,
      "end_time": 341416.0,
      "text": "However, it was my Nigerian heritage that led me to write science fiction."
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 341440.0,
      "end_time": 344960.0,
      "text": "Specifically I cite those family trips to Nigeria in the late &#39;90s."
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 347400.0,
      "end_time": 351936.0,
      "text": "I&#39;d been taking trips back to Nigeria with my family since I was very young."
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 351960.0,
      "end_time": 354536.0,
      "text": "These early trips inspired me."
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 354560.0,
      "end_time": 358280.0,
      "text": "Hence the first story that I ever even wrote took place in Nigeria."
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 358800.0,
      "end_time": 361696.0,
      "text": "I wrote mainly magical realism and fantasy"
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 361720.0,
      "end_time": 363296.0,
      "text": "inspired by my love of Igbo"
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 363320.0,
      "end_time": 366960.0,
      "text": "and other West African traditional cosmologies and spiritualities."
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 368400.0,
      "end_time": 370976.0,
      "text": "However, in the late &#39;90s,"
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 371000.0,
      "end_time": 375216.0,
      "text": "I started noticing the role of technology in Nigeria:"
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 375240.0,
      "end_time": 378960.0,
      "text": "cable TV and cell phones in the village,"
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 378120.0,
      "end_time": 381896.0,
      "text": "419 scammers occupying the cybercafes,"
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 381920.0,
      "end_time": 385336.0,
      "text": "the small generator connected to my cousin&#39;s desktop computer"
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 385360.0,
      "end_time": 387640.0,
      "text": "because the power was always going on and off."
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 388760.0,
      "end_time": 391135.0,
      "text": "And my Americanness othered me enough"
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 391160.0,
      "end_time": 395120.0,
      "text": "to be intrigued by these things that most Nigerians saw as normal."
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 396400.0,
      "end_time": 399320.0,
      "text": "My intrigue eventually gave birth to stories."
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 400320.0,
      "end_time": 402480.0,
      "text": "I started opening strange doors."
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 404480.0,
      "end_time": 407560.0,
      "text": "What if aliens came to Lagos, Nigeria?"
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 410800.0,
      "end_time": 413240.0,
      "text": "This is an excerpt from my novel, \"Lagoon.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 416320.0,
      "end_time": 418296.0,
      "text": "Everybody saw it,"
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 418320.0,
      "end_time": 419920.0,
      "text": "all over the world."
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 420760.0,
      "end_time": 424296.0,
      "text": "That was a real introduction to the great mess happening in Lagos,"
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 424320.0,
      "end_time": 428880.0,
      "text": "Nigeria, West Africa, Africa, here."
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 430360.0,
      "end_time": 433456.0,
      "text": "Because so many people in Lagos had portable, chargeable,"
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 433480.0,
      "end_time": 437896.0,
      "text": "glowing, vibrating, chirping, tweeting, communicating, connected devices,"
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 437920.0,
      "end_time": 441616.0,
      "text": "practically everything was recorded and posted online in some way,"
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 441640.0,
      "end_time": 443135.0,
      "text": "somehow,"
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 443160.0,
      "end_time": 444360.0,
      "text": "quickly."
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 445800.0,
      "end_time": 447960.0,
      "text": "The modern human world is connected like a spider&#39;s web."
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 450400.0,
      "end_time": 451440.0,
      "text": "The world was watching."
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 452200.0,
      "end_time": 454455.0,
      "text": "It watched in fascinated horror"
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 454480.0,
      "end_time": 455800.0,
      "text": "for information,"
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 456560.0,
      "end_time": 458160.0,
      "text": "but mostly for entertainment."
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 459200.0,
      "end_time": 462736.0,
      "text": "Footage of what was happening dominated every international news source,"
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 462760.0,
      "end_time": 467776.0,
      "text": "video-sharing website, social network, circle, pyramid and trapezoid."
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 467800.0,
      "end_time": 469360.0,
      "text": "But the story goes deeper."
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 470800.0,
      "end_time": 471816.0,
      "text": "It is in the mud,"
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 471840.0,
      "end_time": 473376.0,
      "text": "the dirt,"
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 473400.0,
      "end_time": 475135.0,
      "text": "the earth,"
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 475160.0,
      "end_time": 477680.0,
      "text": "in the fond memory of the soily cosmos."
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 478560.0,
      "end_time": 482536.0,
      "text": "It is in the always mingling past, present and future."
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 482560.0,
      "end_time": 484616.0,
      "text": "It is in the water."
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 484640.0,
      "end_time": 488536.0,
      "text": "It is in the powerful spirits and ancestors who dwelled in Lagos."
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 488560.0,
      "end_time": 491880.0,
      "text": "It is in the hearts and minds of the people of Lagos."
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 492720.0,
      "end_time": 495136.0,
      "text": "Change begets change."
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 495160.0,
      "end_time": 496960.0,
      "text": "The alien Ayodele knew it."
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 497720.0,
      "end_time": 499560.0,
      "text": "All her people know it."
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 501200.0,
      "end_time": 505560.0,
      "text": "So, this is a voice of Udide, the supreme spider artist,"
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 505800.0,
      "end_time": 506416.0,
      "text": "who is older than dirt"
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 506440.0,
      "end_time": 509160.0,
      "text": "and lives in the dirt beneath the city of Lagos,"
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 509400.0,
      "end_time": 510976.0,
      "text": "listening and commenting"
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 511000.0,
      "end_time": 514320.0,
      "text": "and weaving the story of extraterrestrials coming to Lagos."
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 515120.0,
      "end_time": 518856.0,
      "text": "In the end, the great spider who was the size of a house"
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 518880.0,
      "end_time": 521816.0,
      "text": "and responsible for weaving the past, present and future"
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 521840.00000000006,
      "end_time": 524559.0,
      "text": "decides to come forth and be a part of the story."
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 525559.0,
      "end_time": 527935.0,
      "text": "Like Udide, the spider artist,"
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 527960.0,
      "end_time": 531135.0,
      "text": "African science fiction&#39;s blood runs deep"
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 531159.0,
      "end_time": 532360.0,
      "text": "and it&#39;s old,"
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 532960.0,
      "end_time": 535216.0,
      "text": "and it&#39;s ready to come forth,"
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 535240.0,
      "end_time": 536816.0,
      "text": "and when it does,"
    },
    {
      "index": 166,
      "start_time": 536840.0,
      "end_time": 541760.0,
      "text": "imagine the new technologies, ideas and sociopolitical changes it&#39;ll inspire."
    },
    {
      "index": 167,
      "start_time": 543520.0,
      "end_time": 547520.0,
      "text": "For Africans, homegrown science fiction can be a will to power."
    },
    {
      "index": 168,
      "start_time": 548840.0,
      "end_time": 550400.0,
      "text": "What if?"
    },
    {
      "index": 169,
      "start_time": 550520.0,
      "end_time": 552000.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s a powerful question."
    },
    {
      "index": 170,
      "start_time": 552600.0,
      "end_time": 553816.0,
      "text": "Thank you."
    },
    {
      "index": 171,
      "start_time": 553840.0,
      "end_time": 558960.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    }
  ]
}